abstract: Chinese officials have confirmed over 7,700 cases of the mysterious illness as foreign governments airlifted their citizens out of Wuhan, the outbreak’s epicenter.
snippet: Chinese officials have confirmed over 7,700 cases of the mysterious illness as foreign governments airlifted their citizens out of Wuhan, the outbreak’s epicenter.
lead_paragraph: Mainland China now has more cases of coronavirus than it had of SARS, a respiratory infection that spread across China in 2002 and 2003 and killed 774 people in 17 countries.  During the SARS outbreak, China had 5,327 cases and 349 deaths, according to the World Health Organization.

abstract: In a striking shift from President Donald Trump’s claim of “perfect” dealings with Ukraine, his defense asserted Wednesday at his Senate trial that a trade of U.S. military aid for political favors — even if proven — could not be grounds for his impeachment.

abstract: With opening arguments wrapped up in President Donald Trump’s impeachment trial, senators will now get a chance to ask questions. But the normally loquacious politicians will still have to keep silent, as their questions can only be submitted in writing.

abstract: Corrections that appeared in print on Wednesday, Jan. 29, 2020.
snippet: Corrections that appeared in print on Wednesday, Jan. 29, 2020.
lead_paragraph: Because of an editing error, an article on Monday about the death of Kobe Bryant misspelled the surname of the chief medical examiner for Los Angeles County. He is Jonathan Lucas, not Luca.

abstract: Republicans won handily a closely watched special election Tuesday to keep hold of a suburban Houston district that President Donald Trump won easily four years ago, fending off a national blitz by Democrats in a Texas legislative race.
snippet: Republicans won handily a closely watched special election Tuesday to keep hold of a suburban Houston district that President Donald Trump won easily four years ago, fending off a national blitz by Democrats in a Texas legislative race.
lead_paragraph: AUSTIN, Texas — Republicans won handily a closely watched special election Tuesday to keep hold of a suburban Houston district that President Donald Trump won easily four years ago, fending off a national blitz by Democrats in a Texas legislative race.
headline_main: GOP Wins Closely Watched Texas Special Election
headline_print_headline: GOP Wins Closely Watched Texas Special Election

abstract: Amy Klobuchar is still fighting to gain ground in Iowa's presidential caucuses that are now just days away.
snippet: Amy Klobuchar is still fighting to gain ground in Iowa's presidential caucuses that are now just days away.
lead_paragraph: COUNCIL BLUFFS, Iowa — Amy Klobuchar is still fighting to gain ground in Iowa's presidential caucuses that are now just days away.
headline_main: Klobuchar Makes Quick Trip to Iowa in Midst of Impeachment
headline_print_headline: Klobuchar Makes Quick Trip to Iowa in Midst of Impeachment

abstract: Democrats who once derided him now want him to testify at President Trump’s impeachment trial while some of his erstwhile Republican friends are throwing him to the curb.
snippet: Democrats who once derided him now want him to testify at President Trump’s impeachment trial while some of his erstwhile Republican friends are throwing him to the curb.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Not long ago, they called him “too extreme,” “aggressively and dangerously wrong” and “downright dangerous.” They called him “nutty,” “reckless” and “far outside the mainstream.”

abstract: Winter typically leaves many parts of New Jersey’s shore deserted, complete with blinking traffic lights and shuttered boardwalk shops, but President Donald Trump’s rally for Rep. Jeff Van Drew jolted Wildwood to life Tuesday, with rally-goers flocking to the seaside resort.

lead_paragraph: WILDWOOD, N.J. — Winter typically leaves many parts of New Jersey’s shore deserted, complete with blinking traffic lights and shuttered boardwalk shops, but President Donald Trump’s rally for Rep. Jeff Van Drew jolted Wildwood to life Tuesday, with rally-goers flocking to the seaside resort.
headline_main: Trump Rally Rouses New Jersey Shore Town to Life
headline_print_headline: Trump Rally Rouses New Jersey Shore Town to Life
